\end_layout

\end_inset

Whenever Teo arrives to a correct checkpoint, congratulates the kid happily
 and prompts him to keep doing a great job.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

The game ends when Teo reaches the final checkpoint.
 
\end_layout

